# 🚦 Smart Traffic Signal RL Environment

## 📌 Problem Statement
Design an AI agent that controls traffic signals to reduce traffic congestion using Reinforcement Learning.

## ⚙️ Approach
- Custom traffic environment
- Q-learning algorithm
- Reward based on waiting time

## 🎯 Features
- 2-way traffic junction
- Adaptive signal control
- Reduced waiting time

## ▶️ How to Run
